# base64

> Encode and decode using Base64 representation
> More information: https://www.unix.com/man-page/osx/1/base64/

- Encode a file:

`base64 --input={file value: plain}`

- Decode a file:

`base64 --decode --input={file value: base64}`

- Encode from stdin:

`echo -n "{string value: plain_text}" | base64`

- Decode from stdin:

`echo -n {string value: base64_text} | base64 --decode`
